title: Killer Kustard Lemon By Vapetasia
description: The best deep, rich, and smooth lemon custard vapor in the e-liquid business is found in Vapetasia's Killer Kustard Lemon e-juice. Every vape of Killer Kustard Lemon will have you smacking your lips in satisfaction because of the flawlessly balanced blend of sweet, sour, and creamy lemon custard flavors it offers. A vape you'll enjoy all day long combines delicious custard creaminess with the ideal hint of slightly sour lemon. There is no wonder why it is the most popular custard flavor e juice in the nation. Fans of Lemon Custard vape juice, you must try this taste!
